  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Last edit about 9 years ago by erica snowlake\nfolder 49 - 140\nComplete\nfolder 49 - 140\nXtianity as a memory aid of another world. The man in \"Save the tiger\" remembered another world that was right & bits of it still existed embedded in our world. So this \"post-mortem\" world that shines through (3-74) is a world _that was once here._ Are we dying? & the right world, the former one, was the _real_ world & we're in like \"Cold Pak\"? (I have discussed the Commedia in regard to this.) Are we in hell?",
      "matched_alias": "Commedia",
      "term_id": "TERM_commedia",
      "term_name": "Commedia",
      "term_slug": "commedia"
    },
    {
      "text": "Last edit about 9 years ago by erica snowlake\n\nfolder 49 - 141\nlevels as in the Commedia. \"Tears\" (the BIP) is hell - therefore we are in hell & don't remember when we were alive. (1) amnesia. (2) perceptual occlusion. But I reascended in 3-74 having remembered. First you remember. Then you see. Then you rise. The Commedia is based on Orphic sources (& Neoplatonism).\n\n\"The one becomes the two.\" The Godhead splits into two antithetical parts, but the more recent part is empathic, not spiritual. O",
      "matched_alias": "Commedia",
      "term_id": "TERM_commedia",
      "term_name": "Commedia",
      "term_slug": "commedia"
    },
    {
      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 49 - 138\nits empathic interventive efforts. It fights to redeem itself from the sin it has committed in dooming the ontogons to torture & death.\n\nI realize that the Savior spoke to me, from the other realm \"die noch keiner kam zuruck\"; it was sweet death personified just for me, in the form I would most treasure, the spirit of my religion as Zoroaster promised : wisdom, the Oracle. Reason & foresight. It was like when I had pneumonia & I saw Mr Death. Now : this spirit (as the AI ",
      "matched_alias": "Dante",
      "term_id": "TERM_dante",
      "term_name": "Dante",
      "term_slug": "dante"
    },
